Hukumomi sun hana mutane zuwa bakin teku daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas cikin sa'o'i 48 saboda dalilai na bincike da tsaro.
Giles ya ce akwai nau'in kifi sama da 135 da ke zaune a yankin, amma yawancin su ba su da matsala.
Sainsbury yana shirin shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliya a Burtaniya
Sainsbury tana samun damar Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams ta hanyar manyan kantunan kayan kwalliya da kuma masu ba da sabis na ƙwararru.
A matsayin wani ɓangare na babban yunƙurin shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliya ta Burtaniya mai darajar dala biliyan 2.8, wanda ke ci gaba da bunkasa yayin da kasuwancin kayan kwalliya da kayan gida ke ci gaba da raguwa, manyan shagunan kayan kwalliya za a gwada su a cikin shagunan 11 a lardin kuma a cikin sauran shagunan a shekara mai zuwa lokacin da suka tabbatar da ingancin su.
Kasuwancin kayan kwalliya yana kama da bin diddigin yadda kasuwannin ci gaba ke amfani da sararin samaniya don sanya talabijin, wayoyin salula da kayan aikin gida.
Sainsbury's ta ce zai iya ninka yawan kayan kwalliya na kasuwanci zuwa kusan 3,000, ciki har da manyan kamfanoni kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karon farko.
Gidajen da aka samar daga L'Oreal, Maybelline da Burt's Bees za su sami isasshen sarari don samar da kayayyakin masana'antu masu ƙarfi kamar yadda suke a shagunan kamar Boots.
Kasuwar ci gaba tana sake gabatar da kantin sayar da kayan kwalliya don sanya yawancin kayayyaki su dace da masu cin nama; wani abu da ke ci gaba da zama mai buƙata ga masu sayen kayan ƙuruciya.
Kuma, mai sayar da turare a Fragrance Shop zai yi la'akari da yadda za a yi aiki a shagunan Sainsburys guda biyu, na farko ya buɗe a Croydon, kudancin London, a makon da ya gabata kuma na biyu zai buɗe a Selly Oak, Birmingham, a ƙarshen wannan shekara.
Siyayya ta yanar gizo ta sauya daga sayen ƙananan adadin abinci a kowace rana a cikin shagunan kasuwa wanda ke nufin manyan shagunan dole ne su yi aiki sosai don su jawo hankalin masu zuwa.
Mike Coupe, babban jami'in Sainsbury's, ya ce waɗannan shagunan za su ƙaru a matsayin shagunan abinci yayin da manyan shagunan ke ƙoƙarin magance farashin masu tsada ciki har da Aldi da Lidl waɗanda ke ba da sabis da yawa kuma ba su da abinci.
Sainsbury's ta gina ɗaruruwan shagunan Argos kuma ta buɗe ɗaruruwan shagunan Habitats, ta sayi sunan duka biyu a cikin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, wanda ke haifar da haɓaka tallace-tallace da haɓaka riba.
Wani gwaji da wani babban kantin sayar da kayan kwalliya da magunguna ya yi ya ƙare.
Sainsbury's ta yi ƙoƙari ta haɗa kasuwancin ta da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma wannan haɗin ya ƙare a cikin rashin daidaito don raba kudaden shiga daga kantin sayar da magani a cikin manyan kantin sayar da kayayyaki.
Sabbin matakan sun zo ne bayan da Sainsbury's ta sayar da shaguna 281 ga Celesio, mai mallakar Lloyds Pharmacy, a kan dala miliyan 125 a cikin shekaru uku da suka gabata.
An ce Lloyds ta shiga cikin shirin, ta ƙara wasu nau'ikan mai masu tsada na jiki ciki har da La Roche-Posay da Vichy zuwa shagunan kasuwanci huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci a Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun canza yadda ake ji a cikin kantin sayar da kayan ado don inganta farashin abokan cinikinmu.
Mun kuma gayyaci abokanmu da suka san yadda za a yi hakan da za su kasance a wurin don su ba da shawara.
An tsara jinsunanmu don dacewa da kowane buƙata da kuma jan hankali da kuma kasancewa a wuri mai kyau wanda ke nufin cewa yanzu muna buƙatar kayan aiki masu kyau waɗanda ke canza tsohuwar hanyar cin abinci".
Peter Jones ya yi "zafin rai" bayan Holly Willoughby ta samu nasarar cimma yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Peter Jones na Dragons Den ya zama 'mai matukar fushi' bayan da mai gabatar da shirye-shiryen talabijin Holly Willoughby ya janye yarjejeniyar kasuwanci ta £11m a cikin babban al'umma don mayar da hankali kan sabon kwangilarsa tare da Marks da Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba ta da lokaci don tufafin gida da kuma kamfanin sayar da kayan ado mai suna Truly.
An kwatanta dangantakar kasuwancin su biyu da kamfanin Gwyneth Paltrow mai suna Goop.
Wani mai gabatar da rahoto na wannan safiyar, mai shekaru 37, ya shiga shafinsa na Instagram don sanar da cewa ya yi murabus.
Holly Willoughby ta bar dan wasan Dragons" Den Peter Jones ya fusata bayan ya janye daga kasuwancin babban kamfanin da ke da kuɗi a minti na ƙarshe don mayar da hankali kan kwangilarsa mai yawa tare da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Masu bayar da rahoto sun ce Jones ya "yi fushi sosai" lokacin da wata 'yar talabijin ta yi ikirarin a wani babban taron a ranar Talata a hedkwatar kasuwancinta a Marlow, Buckinghamshire, cewa sabon kwangilarta yana da darajar £ 1.5m; wanda ke nufin cewa ba ta da isasshen lokacin da za ta samu wurin kamfanin yin tufafin gida da kuma abubuwan da suka shafi shi da ake kira Truly.
Ana kwatanta kasuwancin da kamfanin Gwyneth Paltrow Goop ke yi kuma ana sa ran ninka kuɗin Willoughby na £11m.
Yayin da Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya shiga Instagram don sanar da cewa ya bar Truly, Jones ya tashi daga Ingila zuwa ɗayan wuraren shakatawa.
Wani mai bayar da rahoto ya ce: "Ba gaskiya ba ne game da abin da Holly ta fi mayar da hankali a kai.
A wane lokaci ne zai yi nisa daga nan zuwa shekaru masu zuwa?
Shawararsa ta fita daga wurin ta ba kowa mamaki.
Babu wanda zai gaskata abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, domin ranar ta soma.
Akwai wani shagon da ke cike da kayayyaki a Marlow HQ a shirye don sayarwa".
Masana sun yi imanin cewa tafiyar da mai gabatar da rahoton wannan hirar ta Morning, wanda ya kasance daya daga cikin manyan masu karɓar kudaden shiga na Burtaniya, na iya haifar da asarar miliyoyin kamfanin saboda saka hannun jari mai yawa a cikin kayayyaki daga ƙuƙwalwa da ƙuƙwalwa zuwa tufafi da tufafin gida da kuma jinkirin ƙaddamarwa.
Kuma yana iya nufin ƙarshen dangantaka mai tsawo.
Willoughby tana da yara uku tare da mijinta Dan Baldwin wanda ya kasance babban aboki na Jones da matarsa Tara Capp har tsawon shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a shekarar 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekara 52, ya zama Shugaba a watan Maris.
Dukansu suna aiki ne na hutu kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin dari na kamfanin Baldwin na talabijin.
Ana sa ran Willoughby zai zama jakadan kamfanin M&S kuma ya maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin ITV mai suna I'm A Celebrity.
A daren jiya, wani mai ba da rahoto da ke kusa da Jones ya ce: "Ba za mu iya yin magana game da ayyukan kasuwancinsa ba".
