Tsunami da girgizar kasa a Indonesia sun afkawa tsibirin da suka kashe mutane sama da dari
Alal misali, bayan girgizar ƙasa ta Lombok, an gaya wa ƙungiyoyin gwamnati na duniya cewa ba su da bukata.
Duk da cewa fiye da kashi 10 cikin dari na mazaunan Lombok sun bar gidajensu, ba a taba sanar da wata annoba ta kasa ba, wanda shine farkon buƙatar don samun tallafin duniya.
Mista Sumbung ya ce: "Abin takaici, ya zama bayyane cewa ba za su nemi tallafin duniya ba, don haka yana da wuya.
Yayin da Save the Children ke neman ƙungiyar da za ta yi tafiya zuwa Palu, ba a san ko ma'aikatan kasashen waje za su iya aiki a yankin ba.
Mista Sutopo, mai magana da yawun Cibiyar Kula da Bala'i ta Kasa ta ce hukumomin Indonesia za su duba halin da ake ciki a Palu don ganin ko za a ba da izinin ba da gudummawar tallafi ga kungiyoyin duniya.
Saboda yawan girgizar ƙasa a Indonesia, kasar tana fuskantar bala'i ba tare da shiri ba.
Lokacin da aka gina wani wurin shakatawa na tsunami a Aceh, ba haka yake a sauran yankunan Gulf ba.
Babu wani gargaɗi game da tsunami a Palu, duk da cewa akwai gargaɗi, da alama ya sa mutane suka mutu.
Sau da yawa, yin tafiya tsakanin tsibirin Indonesiya yana da wahala.
Bala'i yana ƙara wahalar kayan aiki.
An ajiye jirgin ruwa mai dauke da asibiti a Lombok don warkar da wadanda suka ji rauni a girgizar kasa a kan hanyar zuwa Palu, amma zai dauki kwanaki uku kafin a kai sabon wurin da ake fama da bala'i.
A lokacin yakin neman zaben, Shugaba Joko Widodo ya lalata ayyukan gyaran kayan aikin Indonesia da suka lalace don a zabe shi kuma ya yi amfani da kudaden da aka kashe don gina hanyoyi da hanyoyin jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin samun kudin shiga don ayyukan daban-daban ya zama sanadiyar rashin nasarar shugabancin Mr Joko yayin da yake neman sake zabarsa a shekara mai zuwa.
Mista Joko kuma yana fama da matsin lamba daga rikice-rikicen addinai a Indonesia inda yawancin Musulmai suka fi bin ƙa'idodin imani na gargajiya.
Fiye da mutane 1,000 ne aka kashe kuma dubban mutane sun bar gidajensu yayin da matasa Kiristoci da Musulmai suka yi yaƙi a kan tituna, ta amfani da ƙaho, kibiyoyi da kibiyoyi da sauran makamai na gargajiya.
Duba: Dan wasan Liverpool Daniel Sturridge ya ci kwallo a wasan Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga gasar cin kofin Ingila ta hanyar ci gaba da cin nasara a Chelsea inda ya ci kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a filin wasa na Stamford Bridge a London.
Sturridge ya samu nasarar buga kwallon daga hannun Xherdan Shaqiri a wani mataki na mita 27 daga filin wasa na Chelsea inda kungiyar ta ci 1-0.
Ball ya juya zuwa hagu kafin ya harbi zuwa kashi na biyu.
Wannan harbi ya kai ga kusurwar dama a saman fasalin.
Sai ƙwallon ya sauko ta wurin Kefas Arzisabala, sai ya ja tarun.
Sturridge ya shaida wa LiverpoolFC.com: "Na sake kokarin zuwa wurin domin samun kwallon kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna wasa ne a kusa da yadda zan iya, don haka na yi kokarin gano yadda zan iya samun kwallon.
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa kuma na taɓa ƙwallon sau ɗaya, ban yi tunani sosai ba kuma na harba".
Chelsea ta ci gaba da ci 1-0 a farkon rabin rabin sa'a bayan da ta ci kwallaye a minti 25 da aka yi wa dan wasan Belgium Eden Hazard.
Wani dan wasan da ke da tufafi masu launin shuɗi ya ba da takardar shaidar ga Mateo Kovacic a wasan, kafin ya gudu zuwa tsakiyar kungiyar zuwa yankin Liverpool.
Kovacic ya tashi ya ba da kwallon a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya jefa wani babban harbi a kan Hazard a shafin yanar gizon.
Hazard ya gudu ya bar mai tsaron gida ya jefa kwallon a raga ta hanyar hannun hagu na Liverpool mai tsaron gida Alisson Becker.
Liverpool ta gamu da Napoli a wasan kungiyoyin gasar zakarun Turai da aka fara da ita da ake kira Champions League da karfe 3 na yamma a ranar Laraba a filin wasa na Stadio San Paolo a Naples, Italiya.
Chelsea za ta gamu da Videoton a gasar Europa League a karfe 3 na yamma a ranar Alhamis a London.
