Gasar da aka ci biyu da aka yi ta hanyar cin nasara ta yi tasiri sosai a wasan, amma Ayr ya cancanci cin nasarar wannan wasan mai ban sha'awa wanda za a iya kira Tennent Day.
Yanzu sun jagoranci jerin, kuma su ne kawai kungiyoyin da ba su yi nasara ba a cikin kungiyoyi goma.
Daga nan sai ya bayyana cewa suna da kariya mai ƙarfi, har ma da sa'a, wanda ya ba wa ƙungiyar da ta karbi bakuncin wasan da kocinta Peter Murchie dalilin farin ciki.
"Mun gwada wasan har zuwa yanzu kuma ba mu yi nasara ba, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki".
Robyn Christie daga Melrose ta ce: "Barka ga Ayr, sun yi nasara a kan mu".
Harbin Grant Anderson a minti na 14, wanda Frazier Climo ya zira kwallaye, ya ba Ayr jagora, amma, katin ja da aka ba wa kyaftin din Scotland Rory Hughes, wanda Warriors ya ba shi don buga wa tawagar, Melrose ya ba shi izinin shiga tawagar tare da Jason Baggot yana ƙoƙarin buga kwallon da aka zira kwallaye.
Climo ya kara da cewa Ayr ya ci nasara a karafin, kafin haka, kafin karshen wasan, ya ci nasara a raga shi kadai kuma ya zama Ayr ta 17-5 a farkon hutun.
Melrose ya fara wasan da kyau a rabi na biyu kuma Patrick Anderson ya ci kwallon daga Baggot, wanda ya rage maki biyar.
Lokacin da aka yi jinkiri a filin wasa saboda mummunan rauni na Ruaridh Knott, wanda aka jefa a cikin wani kwando kuma aka cire shi daga filin wasa, wasan ya sake farawa, inda Ayr ya ci gaba da kusanci kwallon da Stafford McDowall ya zira wa Climo.
A yanzu da aka ba da katin rawaya ga mataimakin kyaftin din Ayr, Blair Macpherson, Melrose ya tura wani dan wasan da ya fi su girma a kwallaye da Bruce Colvine ya zira a baya bayan wasan da ya yi zafi.
A lokacin da kungiyar da ta ci nasara ta biya bashin da ta yi, Struan Hutchinson ya karbi katin rawaya don buga Climo ba tare da kwallon ba, jim kadan bayan layin gidan yanar gizon amahina, MacPherson ya buga kwallon a baya don ya ci Ayr.
Climo ya ci kwallo kamar yadda ya yi a farkon wasan, bayan haka Kyle Rowe ya kama David Armstrong daga shafin yanar gizon kuma ya tura kwallon zuwa ga mai kunnawa Gregor Henry a ƙoƙari na biyar ga ƙungiyar da ta karbi bakuncin wasan.
Wani dan wasan Still Game ya shirya sabon aiki a cikin gidan cin abinci
Mai wasan Still Game Ford Kieran ya bayyana a shirye ya tafi karbar bakuncin bayan ya gano cewa wani jami'in da ke da lasisi a wani kamfanin cin abinci ya gayyace shi.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 56 yana taka rawa a matsayin Jack Jarvis a cikin shahararren shirin BBC, kuma yana rubutu da wasa tare da abokin aikinsa mai suna Greg Hemphill.
Dukansu sun sanar da cewa fim na tara zai zama na karshe a cikin jerin kuma yana da alama Kiernan yana shirin rayuwa bayan Craiglang.
A cewar bayanan da aka bayar, shi ne darektan Adriftmorn Limited.
Mai wasan ya ƙi yin sharhi game da labarin, duk da cewa mai bayar da rahoton ga Scottish Sun ya yi sharhi cewa Kiernan yana son a sanya shi a cikin "kasuwancin cin abinci mai tasowa" na Glasgow.
'Teku na mu ne': ƙasar da ba ta taɓa tekun Bolivia ta yi imanin za ta sake buɗe hanyar zuwa Tekun Fasifik
Jami'an tsaro na ruwa suna da karfi a cikin ruwa da ke zaune a La Paz.
Gidajen gwamnati suna da babban ɗakin kwana mai launin shuɗi.
Masu tsaron ruwa na Titicaca daga yankin Amazon suna da manufa: "Muna da 'yancin zuwa teku.
Muna ɗaukan wannan a matsayin hakki".
A duk faɗin ƙasar da ba ta da ruwa a Bolivia, ana tunawa da wannan lokacin da aka yi nasara a yakin da aka yi a kan tekun da Chile a cikin rikici mai zubar da jini a cikin karni na 19; yayin da ake neman sake yin tafiya a cikin Pacific a wani lokaci.
Wannan shine mafi yawan tsammanin da aka samu a cikin shekarun da suka gabata, yayin da Bolivia ke jiran hukuncin kotun duniya a ranar 1 ga Oktoba bayan shekaru biyar da yanke hukunci.
Roberto Calzadilla, ɗan diflomasiyyar Bolivia ya ce: "Bolivia tana da ƙarfi, ƙungiyar haɗin kai da kwanciyar hankali kuma tana fatan za a yanke shawara mai kyau".
'Yan Bolivia za su duba hukuncin da kotun ICJ ta yanke a kan yankunan da ke cikin kasar, suna fatan kotun Lahe za ta sami hujjar da Bolivia ta yi; bayan shekaru da dama na rashin nasara, inda aka tilasta Shiri ya tattauna yadda za a ba Bolivia damar shiga teku.
Evo Morales, shugaban Bolivia mai basira da kishin kasa, wanda ke neman sake zabarsa a shekara mai zuwa; shi ma yana da tabbacin cewa za a yi nasara a kan hukuncin da aka yanke a ranar Litinin.
A ƙarshen Agusta, ya ce: "Ba mu da lokaci sosai mu koma Pacific Ocean".
Amma wasu masu bincike sun gaskata cewa kotun ba za ta yanke shawara da ta fi dacewa da Bolivia ba kuma ba za ta yi canje -canje ba.
Hukumar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a Netherlands ba ta da ikon bayar da yankin Shiri kuma ta ce ba ta yanke shawarar sakamakon tattaunawar da za a yi ba.
Paz Zárate, masanin shari'ar duniya daga Shiri ya ce: Hukuncin da Kotun ICJ ta yanke ya zo ne watanni shida bayan da shari'ar ta nuna cewa zargin "ba shi da wuya".
Domin ya nuna abin da Bolivia take so, shekaru huɗu da suka shige sun yi watsi da nasarorin da aka samu.
Zárate ya ce: "Bullobalen da ke tattare da ruwa da gwamnatin Bolivia ta yi ya wanzu".
Ya ce, kalmomin da aka yi don yaƙi da Morales sun sa sauran 'yan fashi su yi rashin tausayi.
Bolivia da Chile sun ci gaba da kasancewa da dangantaka, amma zai yi wuya a ci gaba da tattaunawa bayan wannan.
Kasashen biyu ba su yi wa jakadu horo ba tun 1962.
Tsohon shugaban kasa Eduardo Rodríguez Veltzé, wanda ke wakiltar Bolivia a Lahe, ya ƙi shawarar cewa ba a buƙatar yanke hukuncin kotu nan da nan.
A ranar Litinin, zai ba Bolivia " dama ta musamman ta sake kafa sabuwar dangantaka da Shiri" da kuma damar "dakatar da rikici na shekaru 139 da za a amfana daga shi".
Calzadilla ya yi musun cewa Morales, wanda har yanzu yana ɗaya daga cikin shugabannin da suka fi shahara a Amurka ta Tsakiya, zai yi amfani da matsalar aiki a teku don amfanin siyasa.
"Bolivia ba za ta sake cire haƙƙin aiki a Tekun Fasifik ba".
"Wannan shawara ce mai kyau don ganin ko za mu manta da abin da ya faru a baya".
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za a daina samar da makaman nukiliya ba har sai ta amince da Amurka
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa Ri Yong Ho ya ce kasarsa ba za ta daina samar da makaman nukiliya ba idan ba ta amince da gwamnatin Washington ba.
