Ya yi kira ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bi yarjejeniyar da ta bayar a taron da aka yi a Singapore tsakanin shugabannin da ba su yarda ba.
Wannan jawabin ya faru ne a lokacin da Sakataren Harkokin Wajen kasar Mike Pompeo ya yi kusan sake fara tattaunawar nukiliya da aka dakatar bayan watanni uku da tattaunawar da aka yi a Singapore da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa, Kim Jong Un.
