A ranar Lahadi, LeBron zai buga wasan farko na Lakers a San Diego
Ana jiran jiransa ya ƙare yayin da magoya baya ke jiran LeBron James ya fara wasan farko da Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton, ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na gasar a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a tabbatar da adadin mintuna da zai yi wasa ba.
"Za a yi shi a cikin minti 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Wani mai rahoto na Lakers, Mike Trudell, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James zai buga wasanni na mintuna da yawa.
Bayan atisayen da aka yi a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na Lakers na kakar wasa ta gaba na shekara shida.
"Ba na bukatar yin wasannin da suka gabata a wannan matakin da na samu a cikin sana'ata don shirya kaina", in ji shi.
A lokacin da ake gudanar da yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia, a tashar YouTube
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi yakin neman zabe a cikin hadari a daren nan a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne yakin neman zaben Trump na farko a cikin ayyuka biyar da aka shirya a makon gobe, wanda ya hada da yin tafiya a wurare masu ban sha'awa ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ba a gudanar da zaben tabbatar da wanda ya nada shi a matsayin shugaban Kotun Koli ba, Trump yana neman taimako a kan zaben tsakiyar watan da ke tafe tun lokacin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon majalisar dokokin kasar a lokacin zaben a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a yi yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a daren nan kuma ta yaya za a yi amfani da intanet?
An shirya yakin neman zaben Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na safe a ET, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a kan hanyar haɗin yanar gizo na YouTube.
Ana iya ganin Trump yana magana a shari'ar da za a yi a wannan makon game da wanda zai zama shugaban Kotun Koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya karu saboda zargin rashin halayyar jima'i wanda aka yi da za a yi zaben Majalisar Dattijai da ake sa ran amincewa da shi saboda FBI tana bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan yakin shine taimaka wa 'yan Republican su yi nasara a babban zaben Nuwamba don ci gaba da kasancewa da ƙarfi.
Saboda haka, masu neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce, za a gudanar da wannan yakin neman zabe guda biyar a mako mai zuwa domin "karfafa masu aikin sa kai da masu fafutukar neman zabe yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma bunkasa yawan 'yan majalisar dattawa da 'yan majalisa", a cewar rahoton Reuters.
Wani mai magana da yawun Trump ya bukaci Reuters ta ce masa: "Saki na majalisar wakilai muhimmin abu ne a shirinsa na cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin da muke fuskantar babban aikin neman zabe".
Ana sa ran za a yi zanga-zangar a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, wanda a cewar West Virginia Metro News, za a iya tattara masu zanga-zangar daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a buga su a cikin jaridar Pittsburgh".
A ranar Asabar, zai zama ziyarar Trump ta biyu a watan da ya gabata a West Virginia, jihar da ta lashe zaben da kuri'u sama da 40 a shekarar 2016.
Trump yana ƙoƙarin taimakawa dan takarar Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a cikin kuri'un.
"Ba kyakkyawan alama ba ce ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya taimaka masa ya kara yawan kuri'un".
2018 Ryder Cup: Ƙungiyar Amurka ta nuna ƙarfin gwiwa don ci gaba da fatan samun damar yin wasan ranar Lahadi
Bayan shekara ta wasanni, wasan golf na ranar Asabar da yamma na iya zama abin da Ryder ya buƙaci.
Abin farin ciki, an gabatar da ra'ayin wasan kwaikwayo amma yana cikin abin da masu amfani suka amince da shi kuma ba shi da mahimmanci fiye da irin wannan gasar.
To, ina ne ƙarfin nan yake?
"Sun jagoranci da maki shida amma yanzu suna da hudu, don haka ina tsammanin za mu ci gaba da nuna ƙarfi", in ji Jordan Spieth, wanda ya yi tafiya a yamma.
A bayyane yake cewa Turai tana da sa'a, tana da maki hudu a gaba yayin da sauran wasanni 12 za su kasance.
Amurkawa kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, suna jin cewa suna da iska mai ƙarfi da ke damun jiragen ruwa kuma suna da abin sha'awa sosai, aƙalla ba kamar yadda Spieth da Justin Thomas suka yi ba tare da samun maki uku cikin huɗu ba.
Spieth ya ci nasara sosai daga inda ya jefa kwallon a cikin rami mai kyau kuma ya zama misali.
Wannan zai sa su ji daɗin taron da kuma ƙara yawan jama'a yayin da ya buga kwallon ya fada cikin rami, ya ci muhimman maki don kammala wasan yayin da shi da Thomas suka kasance da baya da maki biyu bayan wasanni biyu.
Wasan da ya lashe wasan da ya sa suka ci wasan da 15 a raga ya kuma yi wa jama'a murna, wata hanyar da za a iya tabbatar da cewa ya amince da cewa kungiyar ta Amurka ba ta cikinta.
Spieth ya ce: "Dole ne ka shiga cikin tushen ka kuma damu da wasanka da kanka".
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane ɗan wasan ya rage.
Ramin da za a saka kwallon a ciki 18.
'Yan wasan da suka fi Spieth da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata sune Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, waɗanda suka kasance mafi kyawun' yan wasan Ryder Cup.
Ko da yake akwai iyakar Turai, amma yana da yiwuwar lashe wasanni hudu daga cikin hudu ba tare da wata matsala ba.
"Moliwood" ita ce kawai daga cikin biyu da ba ta iya buga kwallo a ranar Asabar da yamma ba, amma ta ƙi buga kwallo a ramin Asabar da safe, da yammacin Juma'a da kuma a cikin rabin wasan da aka buga a ramin 18 na ranar Juma'a da safe.
Wannan wasa da kuma yadda za su iya motsawa da karfi shine su fita daga cikin ƙungiyar da ta riga ta tabbatar da kansu a matsayin 'yan wasan da za a fuskanta a ranar Lahadi kuma akwai wasu 'yan wasa da suka fi sanannun da za su sa Turai ta ci nasara a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Abin farin ciki, ana iya yin su a hanyoyi dabam dabam.
Ba a yi magana game da cin nasara a Turai ba.
Baban Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi wa jarumin wasan kwallon kafa na safe Sergio Garcia aiki lokacin da Alex Noren ya haɗu da shi.
Yin wasan kwallon kafa biyu zuwa tara ya sa 'yan Spain da Sweden su buga kwallon amma ba su taba yin wasa ba.
Ba wanda zai taimake ka ka cire kwallon daga cikin ramin da ka yi rashin lafiya a ranar Lahadi.
Wasan golf na wasa huɗu yana da ban sha'awa a gani a kusa saboda tattaunawar da ke tsakanin 'yan wasan da ke da alaƙa da juna, shawarwarin da suke bayarwa, shawarwarin da ba su bayarwa da kuma yiwuwar sauya matakan nan da nan.
Turai ta yi nasara a matsayin tawagar har zuwa yau kuma tana da ci gaba da samun maki a ranar karshe amma wasan da 'yan wasa hudu suka yi ya kuma nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ikon yin gwagwarmaya don samun maki; musamman, ga gwamnatocin da ake zargi.
Turai ta jagoranci da maki 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup
Turai na da kyakkyawan fata a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan da ta bayyana a ranar Asabar a wasan da ta buga da kwallo hudu inda ta jagoranci da ci 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Mafi kyawun 'yan wasan Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci wasan da suka ci Tiger Woods mai cin nasara sau biyu don samun lambar yabo ta Le Golf National ta hanyar hudu.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, wadda ta ci gaba da lashe gasar da Hazeltine ya yi shekara biyu bayan haka, ta fi ta Amurka wadda ba ta da kyau a wasan farko na wasan, ta ci nasara da 3-1.
Ƙungiyar Amurka ta nuna kariya a wasanni hudu, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta hana su cin nasara ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas a wasan da aka buga a ranar Lahadi don ya ci gaba da cin kofin.
Fleetwood ya zama dan wasan Turai na farko da ya ci maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari suka sami lakabi na "Molliwood" bayan mako mai ban sha'awa inda su ne kawai 'yan wasan biyu da suka ci maki hudu a farkon wasanni hudu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup.
Gasar da ta yi wa Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan na hudu ta ba shi nasara a kan Woods wanda ba shi da kyau tare da dan wasan farko Bryson Dechambeau inda ya ci 5&4.
Woods, wanda ya buga wasanni biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna babban wasan amma yanzu ya ci nasara a wasanni 19 na wasanni 29 a wasan kwallon kafa hudu da wasanni hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda bai buga wasan dabbobin safe ba, ya sake komawa da Henrik Stenson a wasan hudu da suka yi 2&1 da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, wanda a ranar Laraba ne suka zama masu matsayi na farko a duniya.
Turai ba ta yi wasa ba a cikin farin ciki na yau da kullum, ranar da iska ta fito daga kudu maso yammacin Paris.
An nada masu cin kofin manyan uku Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas a matsayin masu gabatar da Amurkawa na biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci 2&1 a kan 'yan Spain Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a wasan da suka buga hudu kuma suka dawo daga baya suka ci Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasan na hudu bayan sun sha kashi biyu a ramin farko.
Sau biyu a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup ne kawai ƙungiyar da ta ci nasara ta ci nasara ta ci nasara ta ci nasara ta kai ga wasan da aka yi ta hanyar mai wasa ɗaya, kodayake masu cin kofin Furyk kawai suna buƙatar daidaitawa don ci gaba da cin kofin.
Bayan sun kasance masu kyau biyu a cikin kwanaki biyu, amma a ranar Lahadi za su yi wasa da fansa ko da kuwa za su wuce su.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce 'babu wata hanyar' da za ta yi amfani da makaman nukiliya a kasar ba tare da amincewa ba
A ranar Asabar, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ci gaba da sanya takunkumi yana kara karfafa rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma babu wata hanyar da kasar za ta iya dakatar da shirin samar da makaman nukiliya a wannan yanayin.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaidawa jami'an kasa a majalisar dokokin kasar ta shekara-shekara cewa an "yi matakan da suka dace" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya, rushe wuraren gwajin makaman nukiliya da tabbatar da cewa ba za a ci gaba da samar da makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Amma ba mu samu amsar da ta dace ba daga Amurka", in ji shi.
"Babu wani tabbaci ga Amurka cewa za a samu amincewa a cikin tsaron kasarmu kuma idan haka ne ba za mu iya kasancewa a matsayin kasa guda ba don dakatar da samar da makaman nukiliya".
Duk da yake Ri ya maimaita zargin da Koriya ta Arewa ta yi game da matakin da gwamnatin Washington ta dauka na kasancewa a "matakin" na dakatar da makaman nukiliya inda Koriya ta Arewa za ta iya sarrafa kudaden shiga yayin da take motsawa, kalmominsa sun zama masu amfani duk da cewa bai taɓa musun cewa gwamnatin Pyongyang za ta iya dakatar da samar da makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda ta yi a baya.
Ri ya koma ga kalmomin shugabannin biyu, Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump a taron farko na shugaban Amurka mai mulki da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin cewa yana aiki don "dakatar da yin amfani da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin cewa zai kare lafiyar Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta nemi kawo karshen yakin da ta yi a shekarun 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta daina samar da makaman nukiliya.
Gwamnatin Washington ta ki amincewa da rage tsauraran takunkumin da ta dauka a kasar Korea ta Arewa.
Ya ce: "Amurka ta ci gaba da dagewa kan cewa "mu daina samar da makaman nukiliya" kuma ta kara da matakin tsaurara da kuma sanya takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar amfani da karfi, duk da cewa ta ƙi "sanar da ƙarshen yakin".
"Tunanin cewa za a iya yin hukunci a kan mu a kan gwiwa mafarki ne mai ban mamaki ga al'umma da ba ta kula da mu.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da yin hukunci yana ƙarfafa amincewarmu da su".
Ri bai yi wani sanarwa ba game da shirin taron na biyu na Kim da Trump wanda shugaban Amurka ya sake yi a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
A maimakon haka, ministan ya nuna taron uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu, Moon Jae-in, a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya ce: "Idan kasar ta yi la'akari da batun hana samar da makaman nukiliya a yanzu da Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba ce, ba za a dakatar da samar da makaman nukiliya na tsibirin Koriya ba".
Kuma muryar Ri ta bambanta da ta bara, lokacin da ta yi magana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa za a iya harba Amurka da makamai masu linzami na Koriya bayan "Mista Shugaba mai son mugunta" Trump ya kira Kim "mai fashewa" mai shirin kashe kansa.
A taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na wannan shekara, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar "dakatar da" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfinsa na yin matakin dakatar da bama-bamai, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi da kuma kiyaye takunkumin har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta daina yin bama-bamai.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokaci don yin hakan, yana cewa "Idan ya ɗauki shekaru biyu, uku ko watanni uku; ba kome".
Kasashen Sin da Rasha sun yi muhawara da Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kan cewa dole ne ta biya gwamnatin Pyongyang lada saboda matakin da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo, a ranar Alhamis ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro: "Dole ne a ci gaba da tsaurara takunkumin da Kwamitin Tsaro ya ba da kuma ci gaba da yin hakan har sai an tabbatar da cewa an kawar da makaman nukiliya a cikakke, a hankali da kuma a sake duba su".
Majalisar tsaron kasar ta ce ba a taba tsawaita takunkumin da aka sanya wa Koriya ta Arewa tun shekara ta 2006 ba don hana ta samun damar tallafawa gwamnatin Pyongyang a cikin shirin samar da makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wani taron da aka yi a lokacin taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya kuma daga bisani ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma ziyarar da ya yi a baya-bayan nan ba ta yi nasara ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa an dauki mataki, inda 'yan sa'o'i bayan haka Koriya ta Arewa ta sake bayyana cewa "tambaya kamar ta gangami ne".
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin a taron da ta yi da Moon cewa a wannan watan za ta lalata wuraren samar da makaman nukiliya da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta "yi irin wannan aiki".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake son a dauka su ne na tabbatar da tsaro bisa ga yarjejeniyar da Trump ya yi a Singapore kuma yana ci gaba da inganta dangantakarsa da gwamnatin Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyon yadda za su sami isasshen hutu
Wani sabon binciken da Jami'ar Harvard ta gabatar a wannan shekara ya ba da damar samun karin bacci ga duk daliban da ba su kammala karatun digiri na biyu ba don magance yanayin da maza ke ci gaba da kasancewa da shi na yin nazarin kofi tare da 'kowace dare.'
Wani jami'in ya gano cewa ɗaliban da ke kan gaba a jami'a ba su da cikakken bayani game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School da kuma masanin asibitin Brigham da Women's Hospital, ya shirya wani binciken, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shi ne na farko a Amurka da ke da irin wannan shiri.
Ta ba da shawarar fara nazarin bayan ta yi magana game da sakamakon rashin barci a kan halin mutum.
"A ƙarshen tattaunawar, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, 'Me ya sa za a gaya mini haka yanzu, ina cikin shekara ta ƙarshe a kwaleji?'
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba, kuma hakan ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji ta ga jaridar The Telegraph.
A darasi, wanda aka fara bayarwa, an bayyana wa dalibai mahimman abubuwan da ke cikin barci mai kyau wanda ke taimakawa ɗalibai da 'yan wasa suyi aiki da kyau, har ma da inganta rayuwar jama'a.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a sashen likitancin Harvard da kuma babban darektan jami'ar kula da lafiyar jama'a, ya ce jami'ar ta zabi ta kawo wannan darasin bayan da dalibai suka yi bacci na mako guda.
Darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka na sadarwa.
A wani bangare akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke kallon kofi, takalma, takalma na wasanni da littattafai kuma ana gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da ƙarancin barci da kuma muhimmancin samun kyakkyawan bacci.
A wani sashi kuma, an gaya wa masu halartar binciken yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da cututtukan zuciya, bugun jini, ciwon zuciya da ciwon daji.
Taswirar jami'a, wadda take da zane-zane, tana ƙarfafa ɗalibai su yi tunani game da abin da suke yi a kai a kai.
'Mun san cewa ba za su canja halayyar ɗalibai ba.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ce: Amma mun yi imani cewa suna da hakkin sani; kamar yadda kake da hakkin sanin sakamakon lafiyar zabi na shan taba.'
"Har yanzu akwai wani al'ada na yin amfani da 'dare' don koyo", ya kara da cewa, fasaha ta zamani da kuma yawan ɗalibai da ke cewa rashin barci matsala ce mai girma.
Yin aiki don samun isasshen bacci mai kyau, ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' ga ɗalibai don magance damuwa, damuwa da damuwa; da kuma hana kiba, saboda rashin bacci yana sanya kwakwalwa cikin yanayin yunwa, yana haifar da yunwa.
Raymond So, wani dalibi mai shekaru 19 a California wanda ke nazarin kula da lafiyar jiki da kuma ilimin lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler shirya darasi, tun da ya kammala karatunsa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ta ce wannan darasin ya buɗe idanunta kuma ya sa ta so a koyar da ita a dukan jami'o'i.
Ta yi imanin cewa mataki na gaba shi ne a bukaci ɗaliban da suka kammala karatun digiri na biyu su kammala wasu shirye-shirye kafin su shiga cibiyoyin aiki.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da tsara lokacin da za su kwanta da lokacin da za su farka da kuma lokacin da za su san abubuwa masu cutarwa kamar hasken shuɗi na kayan aiki da hasken LED, wanda zai iya sa yanayin barci ya zama mai saurin tashi, wanda zai haifar da matsalolin barci.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Gasar Menga ta kayar da 'yan wasan da Gerrard ya horar
Rangers sun sake yin aikin ido inda Dolly Menga ta ci Steven Gerrard 1-0 a Livingston.
A gefe guda, Ibrox na da alama za ta ci nasara a karo na farko tun lokacin da ta yi nasara a watan Fabrairu a St Johnstone da 4-1, amma Gary Holt ya ci Gerrard a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin shugaba don sa tawagar ta kasance a baya a gasar Ladbrokes bayan Hearts.
Menga ya ci kwallaye a minti bakwai kafin a kammala wasan da Rangers suka yi ba tare da wata makoma ba.
A yanzu da Rangers suka koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ya tashi zuwa matsayi na uku kuma yana bayan Hibernian a kan ci gaba.
Kuma akwai wasu matsaloli da za su iya jiran Rangers bayan da mai tsaron gida, Calum Spence, ya sami rauni a kai bayan wani abu da ya faru ya buge shi daga nesa.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a tawagarsa wanda ya ci Ayr zuwa wasan rabin kofin Red Cup.
Holt, a gefe guda, ya dauki 'yan wasan Livi 11 da suka ci Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma ya yi farin ciki da yadda tawagar ta ci gaba da buga wa abokan gaba a duk wasan.
Rangers na iya zama na musamman a kwallon amma Livingston ya samar da mafi ƙarancin kwallon da aka samu.
Sun ci nasara a cikin 'yan mintoci kaɗan lokacin da aka jefa kwallon farko ta Menga zuwa filin Allan McGregor amma dan wasan tsakiya ya samu damar jefa kwallon a waje.
An jefa kwallon kwallon kafa a cikin tsakiya ta Keaghan Jacobs wanda ya sami mai tsaron gida, Craig Halkett, amma dan wasan baya Alan Lithgow ya fitar da kwallon daga tsakiya.
Rangers sun jagoranci wasan amma ya zama kamar ya kamata su yi aiki fiye da yadda suka yi a wasan karshe na karshe.
Babu shakka, Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya cancanci a yi masa hukunci a minti na 75 a lokacin da ya yi wasan da Steven Lawless, amma mai shari'a, Steven Thomson, ya ƙi ya yi la'akari da abin da ɗan ƙasar ya faɗa.
Rangers sun ci gaba da harbi biyu kawai a cikin tseren a farkon rabin rabin amma tsohon mai tsaron gidan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, bai yi watsi da ƙwallon ƙafa da Lassana Coulibaly ya yi ba da kuma rashin daidaituwa na Ovie Ejaria.
Idan har da bugun farko na Livi a minti na 34 na iya zama sakamakon bugun, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa bai kamata a ci shi ba kuma a bi tsarin da aka tsara.
Rangers kuma sun kasa dawo da wasannin tsaro da Jacobs ya yi.
Scott Arfield bai taɓa ƙwallon ba wanda Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson, wanda bai taɓa yin wani abu ba don dakatar da ƙwallon da Menga ya sanya a cikin sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu lokacin da ya sauya Coulibaly zuwa Ryan Kent, wanda ya kasance da sakamako na nan take lokacin da aka ba da ƙwallon ga Morelos amma Kelly ya yi nasara kuma ya dakatar da ƙwallon.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da ƙin ƙungiyar da ta ziyarce shi don buga wasan kwallon kafa na yau da kullun, inda Lithgow da Halkett suka buga manyan ƙwallon ƙafa.
Holt ya ci wani kwallo a minti na ƙarshe amma McGregor ya tsaya a tsaye ya hana Jacobs buga kwallo lokacin da Lithgow ya jefa kwallo a waje.
Rangers sun maye gurbin Glenn Middleton wanda ya yi ikirarin cewa ya kamata a yi hukunci a kan Jacobs amma mai shari'a Thomson ya yi watsi da hakan.
Almanac: Wanda ya kirkiro Geiger Counter
Har ma da shafinmu na "Sunday Morning" Almanac: 30 ga Satumba, 1882, kwanaki 136 sun shude a yau kuma muna da KYAUTA... ranar da aka haifi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, mai zaman kansa a nan gaba a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wani tsari na ganowa da kuma kimanta sakin kwayoyin halitta, wanda ya haifar da wani kayan aiki da ake kira Geiger Counter.
An kafa wannan na'urar a kimiyyar kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, kuma an kafa ta a matsayin Geiger Counter a cikin wasan kwaikwayo, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya ƙunshi roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mijin: "Wane irin kayan aiki ne?"
Rogers: "Gigager Counter ne, wanda ake amfani da shi wajen gano abubuwa masu ƙarancin ƙwayoyin cuta kamar su iranium.
Idan ka ba ni wannan na'urar, za ka iya fahimtar yadda kwayoyin halitta suke juyawa daga kwayoyin halitta da ke cikin waɗannan duwatsu masu daraja".
Evans: "Sai suka soma tsallewa!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma, har ila ana amfani da ƙarfe da aka kira sunansa.
Sabuwar allurar cutar kansa na iya koya wa jikin mutum ya "sami" ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa
Sabon allurar kansa na iya koya wa tsarin jiki ya "sami" ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa kuma ya kashe mu
Allurar rigakafi tana koyar da tsarin jikin mutum don gano kwayoyin cutarwa a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani
Wannan tsarin yana cire kwayoyin halitta da ke taimaka wa mutum ya zama mai haƙuri kuma ya mai da su dakin gwaje-gwaje
Za su iya "sami" furotin da ke cikin cututtukan daji da yawa kuma su sake yin amfani da shi a cikin jiki.
Gwajin da ake yi na gwaji yana nuna sakamako mai gamsarwa ga marasa lafiya masu fama da ciwon daji daban-daban.
Wata mace ta samu rigakafin da ya taimaka wa jikin ta gane kwayoyin cutar, wanda ya taimaka mata ta warke daga cutar kansa bayan watanni 18.
Ana amfani da shi don cire ƙwayoyin halitta daga cikin mai haƙuri, kuma a juya su zuwa dakin gwaje-gwaje don "sami" furotin da ake kira HER2 wanda yake cikin yawancin cututtukan daji kuma a sake yin amfani da ƙwayoyin halitta a cikin jiki.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka ta National Cancer Institute a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Binciken da muka samu ya nuna cewa muna da ingantaccen allurar rigakafi".
Farfesa Berzofsky ya bayyana cewa HER2 "yana haifar da ci gaban nau'ikan cututtukan daji da yawa", ciki har da ciwon nono, ciwon huhu, da ciwon sukari.
Wata hanyar da za a cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin mai haƙuri da kuma "koyar" waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta don magance ƙwayoyin cuta na asali an yi amfani da su wajen magance cutar sankarar jini.
Kanye West ya yi magana mai ban sha'awa ga magoya bayan Trump, yana sanye da hular da ya rubuta MAGA, bayan ya bayyana a shirin SNL.
Ba a yi nasara ba
Kanye West ya yi ihu a cikin gidan rediyo a cikin shirin Saturday Night Live bayan wani mummunan raira waƙa da ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump, kuma ya ce zai yi takara a zaben shugaban kasa na 2020.
Bayan ya rera waƙar sa ta uku a daren, ya kira Ghost Town a cikin rigar Make America Great, kuma ya yi wa 'yan Democrat tawaye kuma ya sake bayyana goyon bayansa ga Trump.
"Na yi magana sau da yawa game da fararen fata, suna cewa, 'Yaya za ka so Trump, ba za ka yi wani abu ba?'
"Idan ina damuwa da tsunduma, to na bar Amurka ne a baya".
Shafin SNL ya fara da wani wasan kwaikwayo wanda ya hada da sukar da aka yi da shahararren dan wasan Hollywood Matt Damon inda ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh kafin Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai ya amsa zargin da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi game da cin zarafin jima'i.
Duk da cewa ba a buga shi a cikin jaridu ba, an sanya hotunan kalmomin da aka yi wa West a kan dandalin yanar gizo ta hanyar ɗan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock.
Ba a bayyana ko Rock ya yi niyyar sukar West ba bisa ga abin da ya wallafa.
Kuma West ya yi nadama cewa masu sauraron taron sun yi magana da yawa a bayan fage a kan kwalkwali da ya sa.
"Sun bi ni a bayan dandalin.
Sun ce, 'Kada ka shiga dandalin wasa da kwalkwali'
Sun bi ni!
"Sai suka ce ba zan tsaya ba", in ji Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Kuna son in ga cewa ba ni da wani wuri?" ya ce "don in sa hular shugaba, domin yana nufin ba za ku gaya mini abin da zan yi ba. Kuna son duniya ta ci gaba?
