Dan wasan wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya yi tir da halin da ake ciki na kibago
Kit Harington ya shahara sosai a matsayin mai daukar takobi a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin jerin jerin jerin abubuwan da aka yi a cikin jerin shirye-shiryen talabijin na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma 'yar wasan mai shekara 31 ta yi tir da nuna bambanci game da wannan jarumin, tana cewa wasan yana nufin cewa matasa suna jin cewa dole ne su ci gaba da kasancewa da mutunci.
A wata hira da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa 'akwai wani abu da bai yi daidai ba' kuma ya yi mamakin yadda zai magance matsalar rashin ɗabi'a ta maza yayin da aka kaddamar da yakin neman 'yancin mata da ake kira #Me.
Kit, mai shekara 31, wanda kwanan nan ya auri actress Rose Leslie a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, ta yarda cewa tana jin 'ƙasa sosai' game da warware matsalar.
'Ina jin kaina ina da iko sosai a yanzu, ina tambaya, 'Shin daga wane wuri ne irin wannan halin maza ya fito?
'Shin muna koyar da maza idan sun girma, game da matsalolin da muke fuskanta yanzu?'
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na karuwar lalata ta maza saboda yawan masu fim da ke nuna lalata.
Ya ci gaba: 'Me mutum yake nufi a haife shi?
Menene ake koyarwa a talabijin, kuma menene ake koyarwa a titi, da zai sa matasa su ji cewa suna da wani ɓangare na zama maza?
Ina ganin wannan tambaya ce mai muhimmanci a zamaninmu: Ta yaya za mu gyara waɗannan?
