A cikin hira, ya yarda cewa ba zai iya yin wasan kwaikwayo na farko ko na gaba na Game of Thrones ba lokacin da za a kammala wasan kwaikwayon a wannan bazarar, yana cewa 'ba ya son yaƙi da hawan doki.'
Daga watan Nuwamba Kit zai taka rawa a cikin wani labari na Sam Shepard mai suna True West wanda shine labarin mai shirya fim tare da ɗan'uwansa mai sata.
A kwanan nan, wani dan wasan kwaikwayo ya sanar da cewa ya ga cewa saduwa da matarsa, Rose, shine mafi kyawun sakamako daga jerin wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
Ya ce: 'Na sadu da matata a cikin wani fim, don haka na ba da iyalina gaba da sabuwar rayuwata tun daga wannan lokacin.'
Rose ta yi aiki da sunan Ygritte, wanda Kit ya fi so a matsayin Jon Snow, a cikin jerin shirye-shiryen Emmy Award.
