Cutar AIDS: China ta ce an samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na sabon kamuwa da cutar
Kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14% na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kuma wadanda ke dauke da cutar kanjamau.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 sun kamu da cutar a kasar, a cewar hukumomin kiwon lafiya.
Kimanin mutane 40,000 ne aka samu a kashi na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sabbin cututtuka sun kamu da cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da yadda ya kasance a baya.
A wasu sassan kasar Sin, cutar AIDS tana yaduwa cikin sauri saboda zubar da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar ta HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili, jami'an kiwon lafiya a kasar Sin sun sanar a wani taron da aka gudanar a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar AIDS a kasar Sin yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce ga masu jima'i a kasar Sin.
An haramta jima'i tsakanin maza da mata a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana nuna wariya ga maza da mata.
Domin al'ummar da ke bin ka'idoji na zamani, binciken ya kiyasta cewa 70-90% na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza sun kai ga yin aure da mata.
Yawancin cututtukan cututtuka na jima'i suna faruwa ne ta hanyar jima'i ba tare da isasshen kariya ba a cikin wannan aure.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun maganin cutar AIDS a duniya a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
