Gwamnatin Washington na iya "idan ya zama dole" ta yanke shawarar amfani da jiragen ta na soja don hana iskar gas daga Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da dama, gami da Gabas ta Tsakiya, a cewar Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
