Ronaldo ya musanta zargin fyade yayin da jami'an shari'a ke shirin kai wani jaridar Jamus kotu
Cristiano Ronaldo ya bayyana zargin da ake masa na fyade a matsayin "ruwaye", yana mai cewa mutane "suna son su bayyana kansu" ta hanyar amfani da sunansa.
Lauyoyinsa na shari'a suna shirin yin karar jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wadda ta wallafa zargin.
An zargi dan wasan Portugal da Juventus da yin fyade da fyade da aka yi wa wata 'yar Amurka mai suna Kathryn Mayorga a wani otal a Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
An ce ya biya shi dala 375,000 domin ya yi shiru ba zai yi magana ba, kamar yadda jaridar Der Spiegel ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
A cikin wani bidiyo na kai tsaye a Instagram yana magana da mabiyansa miliyan 142 'yan sa'o'i bayan da aka gabatar da zargin, Ronaldo, mai shekaru 33, ya musanta wannan bayanin yana mai da shi "ruɗu".
"A'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, a'a.
Abin da suka ce a yau, labari ne mai zurfi", in ji mai lashe kyautar Ballon d'Or sau biyar a gaban kyamarar.
"Suna son su san kansu da sunana.
Hakan na faruwa.
Suna son a san su da sunana, amma wannan wani ɓangare ne na aikinmu.
Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma kome yana da kyau", in ji shi da murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin yin tuhuma da jaridar Der Spiegel ta wallafa zargin, wanda suka kira shi "ba bisa ka'ida ba na zargin sirri", a cewar kamfanin dillancin labaran Birtaniya na Reuters.
Wani lauya mai suna Christian Schertz ya ce dan wasan ya nemi fansa don "rashin mutuntakarsa da ta haifar da rashin adalci, wanda zai iya zama babban abin takaici ga 'yancin ɗan adam a shekarun baya".
An yi zargin cewa an kai karar ne a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009 a otal din Palms Hotel and Casino a Las Vegas.
Bayan ganawarsu a cikin ɗakin kwana, Ronaldo da Mayorga an ruwaito sun koma ɗakin dan wasan, inda aka yi zargin sun yi masa fyade a cikin kwanyar, a cewar takardun da Kotun Koli ta Clark County, Nevada ta bayar.
Mayorga ya ce Ronaldo ya durƙusa bayan wannan kuma ya ce "99 bisa dari" shi "mai kyau ne" kuma "wani abu ne da ya sa ya yi sanyin gwiwa".
Takardun sun nuna cewa Ronaldo ya yarda cewa su biyun sun yi jima'i, amma sun yarda da hakan.
Mayorga ta ce ta je ofishin 'yan sanda kuma tana da hotunan da aka yi wa raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga baya ta amince ta magance matsalar ba tare da zuwa kotu ba saboda tana jin "tsoron tashin hankali" kuma tana damuwa da "yancin da za a yi mata a fili".
Wani dan wasan dan wasan mai shekaru 34 ya ce yanzu yana neman sauya yarjejeniyar domin ya ci gaba da damuwa da abin da ya faru.
Ronaldo ya kusan komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United a lokacin da ake zargin cewa ya rasa wani kuma a wannan bazarar ya koma babbar kungiyar Juve a kan dala miliyan 100.
Ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai Birtaniya da aka sani da Brexit: Birtaniya na iya 'ƙaddamar da kanta har abada' bayan ta rasa masana'antar kera motoci
Birtaniya "za ta iya yin nadama har abada" ta rasa sunan farko a duniya a cikin kera motoci bayan barin Tarayyar Turai, a cewar Sakataren Kasuwanci Greg Clark.
Ya kara da cewa "yana da matukar damuwa cewa kamfanin Toyota na Burtaniya ya shaida wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar EU babu wata yarjejeniya da za ta dakatar da samar da motoci a cikin masana'antar ta a Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
Clark ya ce: "Muna bukatar mu fahimci juna".
Wani kamfanin kera motoci na kasar Japan ya ce sakamakon jinkirin a kan iyaka zai iya faruwa idan rashin jituwa a lokacin da Birtaniya ta kasance cikin EU ya haifar da rashin aikin yi.
Kamfanin Burnaston; mai kera motocin Toyota Auris da Avensis, ya samar da motoci kusan 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata wanda kashi 90% na motocin da aka fitar da su aka fitarwa zuwa kasashen EU.
Marvin Cooke, shugaban kamfanin Toyota a Burnaston ya ce: "A ganina, idan Birtaniya ta bar EU a karshen watan Maris, za a yi amfani da masana'antar kera motoci a masana'antarmu".
Wasu masana'antun kera motoci a Burtaniya sun nuna fargaba cewa barin Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba game da kasuwancin da ba a iyakance ba, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover.
Alal misali, BMW ta ce za ta rufe wani karamin masana'anta a Oxford bayan wata guda da Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai.
Babban abin damuwa shine masana'antun kera motoci suna da'awar cewa hanyar da suke samun kayan aiki shine ta hanyar sayar da kayayyaki masu matsala yayin da rashin daidaito ya faru bayan da Burtaniya ta bar EU.
Toyota tana aiki ne don "rage lokacin samar da motoci, inda kayan aiki ke zuwa kowane minti 37 daga masu gyara ko dai a Burtaniya da EU don samar da motoci da aka yi wa oda.
Lokacin da Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga Maris, za a iya samun dakatarwar aiki a cikin takaddama inda masana'antar ta ce hakan zai haifar da jinkiri da kuma rashin kayan aiki.
Ba zai yiwu ba Toyota ta ajiye motocin da aka yi a rana guda a shagon da take da shi a wani masana'anta a Derbyshire, kamfanin ya ce kuma zai iya dakatar da samar da motocin.
Mista Clark ya ce shirin Theresa May na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai ya ƙunshi tsare-tsaren da ake yi game da dangantakarsa da Tarayyar Turai "wanda aka gyara sosai don hana a yi tsananin kula da kan iyaka".
"Dole ne mu cimma yarjejeniya. A cikin hira da BBC Radio 4 ta yau, ya ce: Muna fatan mu cimma yarjejeniya mai kyau wanda zai ba mu damar cimma burinmu kawai a wannan kakar amma kuma ya ba mu damar samun damar".
"A bayyane yake cewa ba kawai ga Toyota ba har ma da sauran masana'antun kera motoci inda muke buƙatar ci gaba da kasancewa da damar samun kayan aiki da kuma samar da kayayyaki masu kyau".
Toyota ba ta iya bayyana lokacin da za a dakatar da samar da motoci ba, amma a cikin dogon lokaci, ta yi gargadin cewa karuwar farashin zai rage ƙarfin masana'antar a kasuwa kuma ba zai haifar da rashin aikin yi ba.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston na tsawon shekaru 24 kuma yana cikin ƙungiyar ma'aikata a wurin, ya ce, "A ra'ayina, idan aka cire wasu ayyuka, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
"Dole ne mu kafa wani shiri mai karfi da tabbaci na makomarmu ga dangantakarmu da Tarayyar Turai", in ji wani kakakin gwamnatin.
A cewar Ofishin Shugaban Amurka, ana iya sake hana taron Trump da Rosenstein
Babban taron Donald Trump da babban jakadan gwamnatin kasar, Rod Rosenstein, na iya "kasancewa zuwa mako guda" yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar da za a yi wa babban wakilin allurar rigakafi, Brett Kavanaugh; Ofishin Shugaban Amurka ya sanar da hakan a wannan Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da ayyukan mai ba da shawara mai zaman kansa Robert Mueller, wanda ke bincika tsoma baki na Rasha a cikin zaben, tarurruka tsakanin magoya bayan Trump da Rasha da kuma kasancewa shugaban kasa don hana shari'a yin aikinta.
Ko zai yiwu ko ba zai yiwu ba Trump ya kori babban wakilin gwamnati, har ma da barazanar da zai iya haifar da 'yancin kai na Mueller, ya haifar da jita-jita a Washington na tsawon watanni.
A farkon watan nan, New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya yi zargin cewa ya sa belun kunne don yin rikodin tattaunawar da ya yi da Trump da kuma yiwuwar za a yi wa shugaban kasa zaben bisa ga Dokar Kwaskwarima ta 25 na Tsarin Mulki na Amurka.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan sanarwa.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya je ofishin shugaban Amurka, inda ake zargin cewa zai yi murabus.
A maimakon haka, an sanar da taron da ya yi da Trump, a hedkwatar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York, a ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce ya "zaɓa" kada ya kori Rosenstein amma yanzu an soke shawarwarin sulhu saboda ya guji ganawa da Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da shari'ar da Kavanaugh da ɗaya daga cikin matan da ke zarge shi da lalata ta jima'i, Dr Christine Blasey Ford, suka ba da shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya bukaci FBI ta binciki zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda ya kara jinkirta zaben majalisar dattawa.
Sakataren yada labarai na Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a tashar talabijin ta Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
A lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da shawarwarin Rosenstein, ya ce: "Ba a amince da kwanan wata ba, mai yiwuwa a wannan watan, kuma ana iya jinkirta shi zuwa wata mako saboda sauran al'amuran da ke faruwa a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu ga abin da zai faru kuma zan ci gaba da ba da labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi watsi da rahoton: Sanders bai yi kira ga taron a ofishin shugaban Amurka ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai watsa shiri Chris Wallace ya yi mamakin dalilin.
Sanders ya ce rashin jin daɗin sabon jaridar ba don ƙin nuna sha'awar 'yan jaridar TV ba ne "saboda halin rashin halayensu", duk da cewa ya ce: "Ba na yarda da shi ba domin yana cewa suna da halayyar rashin halayyar".
Ya kuma ce, ana samun karin tattaunawa tsakanin Trump da kafofin yada labarai.
"Shugaba yana da tambayoyi da amsoshi fiye da kowane shugaban da ya riga shi", ya ce, ya ƙara da cewa: "Mun duba waɗannan ƙididdigar".
Har ila yau, tattaunawar da ake yi don samun sabon labari tana ci gaba, a cewar Sanders, amma "idan kafofin watsa labarai sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, ya fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sau da yawa kuma kun ga muna yin hakan a makonni da suka gabata kuma zai dauki lokaci na bayar da sabon bayani lokacin da zaku iya tuntuɓar shugaban Amurka".
A al'ada, Trump yana amsa tambayoyi lokacin da yake barin ofishin shugaban Amurka ko kuma yana amsa tambayoyin da aka yi masa ko kuma a taron manema labarai da manyan jami'an suka ziyarce shi.
Ba a yawan samun tattaunawa da kafofin watsa labarai a kan kansa.
A wannan makon a New York, shugaban ya bayyana dalilin, inda ya yi ta karya doka kuma a wasu lokutan ya bayyana a gaban taron manema labarai.
Sakataren lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan kungiyar Turai da ke aiki a NHS Scotland game da tsoron cewa Birtaniya za ta fice daga kungiyar
Sakataren lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan kungiyar ta EU da ke aiki a NHS a Scotland yana nuna godiya da fatan kasar ta ci gaba da aiki bayan Birtaniya ta bar kungiyar.
Jeane Freeman, memba na majalisar dokokin Scotland ta aika da wasiƙar kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fita daga Tarayyar Turai.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta amince da biyan kuɗin da 'yan ƙasar Tarayyar Turai ke biya don ayyukan da ta yi.
A cikin wasiƙar da ta rubuta, Ms. Freeman ta ce: "A lokacin rani, tattaunawar da ke tsakanin Birtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, suna tattauna shawarar da ake tsammani a wannan fannin.
Amma gwamnatin Burtaniya ta kara karfafa ayyukanta na shiri a lokacin da babu yarjejeniya.
Na san cewa lokaci ne mai wuya a gare mu duka.
Saboda haka ina so in sake yin magana game da wannan a yanzu don nuna yadda nake daraja gudummawar kowane ma'aikaci, ko da wane irin ƙasa ne.
Abokan aikina daga ƙasashen EU suna kawo kwarewa da ilimi masu amfani waɗanda ke haɓaka da inganta aikin kiwon lafiya da kuma amfanin marasa lafiya da kuma kungiyoyin da muke ba da sabis.
Babu shakka, Scotland tana cikinku kuma muna son ku zauna a wurin".
