Dan wasan baya na Tennessee State Tigers, Christion Abercrombie, ya yi gaggawa bayan ya yi rauni a kan kai a wasan Asabar da suka yi 31-27 a hannun Vanderbilt Commodores, a cewar mai magana da yawun Tennesseean Mike Organ.
Kocin Tennessee State Rod Reed ya shaida wa manema labarai cewa wannan rauni ya faru ne jim kadan kafin ya yi ritaya a kakar wasa ta farko.
Reed ya ce: "Ya yi tafiya a gefe kuma ya faɗi".
Masu horarwa da likitoci sun kara yawan iskar oxygen na Abercrombie a kusa da filin wasa kafin a sanya shi a cikin kwandon kuma a kai shi don ƙarin bincike.
Wani ma'aikacin tawagar Tennessee State ya shaidawa Chris Harris, mai rahoto na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee, cewa Abercrombie ya bar asibitin da ake yi masa a Vanderbilt Medical Center.
Harris ya kara da cewa "babu wani bayani game da yawan rauni da tsawon lokacin da zai yi" kuma Tennessee State tana kokarin gano lokacin da rauni ya faru.
Abercrombie, mai shekara ta biyu, ya yi wasa a Tennessee State a shekara ta farko bayan ya samu wata canja wuri daga Illinois.
A ranar Lahadi, ya yi bugun jini kafin ya fita daga wasan, inda ya yi nasarar yin bugun jini guda 18.
