Girgizar ƙasa ta afku a Sulawesi ta tsakiyar lokaci a arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Ana samun bidiyo a shafukan yanar gizo na duniya game da lokacin da girgizar ta fara.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a wani gidan wasan kwaikwayo na sandstone a birnin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya kai ga bakin teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na gwamnati za su nemi hukuncin kisa wanda ba a bayar da shi ba don kawo karshen harin ta'addanci a birnin NYC
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York za su nemi hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da aikata harin kai-kai a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas; ba a taɓa yin hukuncin kisa a jihar ba saboda laifin da aka yi wa al'umma tun 1953.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don yin barazanar da ta kai wa masu wucewa a kan babbar hanyar West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu hawa da kuma masu hawa keke barazanar a watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar neman hukuncin kisa, da aka gabatar a kotun kudancin New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan suna iya kaiwa ga hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun kasar ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22 wadanda suka hada da laifin kashe mutane takwas da suka taimaka wajen samun kudi ba bisa ka'ida ba, wadanda masu gabatar da kara suka yi amfani da su a shari'ar aikata laifuka da kuma laifin lalata da motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirya da ganganci", kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi amfani da "harin da ya fi tsanani, da kuma mummunan hali".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya raunana, ya raunana da kuma kashe dangin da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", a cikin sanarwar da ta bayyana manufarsa.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu a harin 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shige tun lokacin da kotun gundumar New York ta yanke hukuncin kisa.
An samu wanda ake zargi, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe 'yan kasuwa biyu na miyagun ƙwayoyi amma daga bisani an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai a watan Satumba na 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kotun New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, an yanke wa ma'aurata da suka yi aure hukuncin kisa a kan zargin yin leken asiri ga tsohuwar Tarayyar Soviet shekaru biyu kafin yakin basasa.
An kashe Rosenbergs ta hanyar amfani da kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna cewa bai yi nadama ba game da abin da ya yi a cikin watanni bayan harin, bisa ga takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji dadi saboda abin da ya yi, kamar yadda 'yan sanda suka ruwaito.
Saipov ya shaida wa jami'an cewa ya yi tunanin kai hari ne bayan ya kalli bidiyon kungiyar ta'addanci ta ISIS a wayarsa, bisa ga takardar da ke dauke da zargin.
Ya kuma bukaci a nuna wani rukunin 'yan ta'adda na ISIS a dakin asibitin da yake, kamar yadda 'yan sanda suka ruwaito.
Ya yi shari'a a kan zargin da aka yi masa na 22 ba tare da ya yarda ba.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "ya yi matukar damuwa" da hukuncin da masu gabatar da kara suka yanke.
Patton ya ce: "Muna ganin cewa hukuncin da ake nema na yanke hukuncin kisa maimakon ya amince da zargin da ake masa zai yi masa a kurkuku har abada ba tare da wata hanyar da za a iya sake shi ba zai sake zama abin takaici ga duk wadanda abin ya faru".
Kungiyar kare laifin da ake tuhuma da shi, Saipov, ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da su daina yanke masa hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Tory ya ce dole ne a ba NIGEL FARAGE nauyin yin shawarwari kan yadda za a bar Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai
Nigel Farage ya yi niyyar 'karfafawa jama'a' a yau a zanga-zangar da ke gudana a wurin taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Ukip ya ce 'yan siyasa su yi watsi da 'tashin hankali' daga sukar EU, inda wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Theresa May da kanta ta ce ya kamata ya kasance a cikin tattaunawa da EU.
Wani dan majalisa mai zaman kansa mai zaman kansa, Peter Bone, ya shaida wa masu ziyara a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya ta "fita daga cikin al'umma" yanzu da Mista Farage ya zama Sakataren ayyukan fitar da Birtaniya daga EU.
Amma matsalar da Mrs May ta fuskanta ita ce ta haɗa abokan aikinta da ra'ayoyi daban-daban wanda zai sa 'yan Tory da ke son su kasance a cikin EU su shiga wani zanga-zanga na birane na neman Birtaniya ta bar EU.
Firayim Minista yana fama da ci gaba da aiwatar da shirinsa na cire Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai yayin da yake fuskantar hare-haren masu son Birtaniya daga EU da kuma masu son zama a cikin EU.
Abokan hulɗar sun ci gaba da cewa zai ci gaba da ƙoƙarin neman sasantawa da Belgium duk da cewa wasu ba su yi farin ciki ba, kuma sun tilasta masa ya soki Tarayyar Turai da kuma jam'iyyar Labour don su yanke shawara kan shawarwarin da suka dace.
Mista Bone ya shaida wa masu halartar shirin Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son 'dakatar da shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai'.
Ya ce dole ne a shigar da Mista Farage kuma a ba shi aikin yin shawarwari da Belgium.
'Da a ce shi ne shugabanmu, da mun riga mun fita.'
'Zan yi kira ga Birtaniya ta fita daga Tarayyar Turai amma muna bukatar mu soke shirin Birtaniya na fita daga Tarayyar Turai,' in ji 'yan majalisar Wellingborough.
Da yake magana game da matsayin da yake da shi na Tarayyar Turai, ya ce: 'Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya ba don nuna rashin ƙarfi.
Muna son mu kafa dokoki a ƙasarmu.'
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da bukatar jama'a tun zaben 2016: 'Tunanin cewa 'yan Birtaniya sun canza ra'ayi kuma suna son su kasance cikin al'umma ba gaskiya bane.'
Wani dan Tory wanda ke son Birtaniya ta bar EU, Andrea Jenkyns, ya kasance a cikin wannan tafiya, ya ce wa manema labarai: 'Abinda kawai nake so in ce shi ne: Firayim Minista, ku saurari jama'a.
"Manufar da Birtaniya ta yi na barin Tarayyar Turai ba ta da kyau a cikin al'umma, 'yan adawa ba za su zabe ta ba, ba ta da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu kuma masu canjin da muke aiki tare da su a kan titi ne ke sa mu a matsayin masu jefa kuri'a.
Ka fara sauraron wannan shirin.'
A cikin irin wannan sakon da aka aika wa Mrs. May, ya ce: 'Prime Ministers suna ci gaba da aikinsu idan sun cika yarjejeniyar.'
Mista Farage ya gaya wa 'yan siyasa a kan tafiya cewa dole ne su ji 'tsananin' idan za mu yi wa shawarar da aka yanke a zaben 2016.
Ya ce: "Yanzu abin da ya rage shi ne amincewa tsakaninmu, jama'a da kuma bangaren siyasa".
"Suna kokarin yin ta'addanci kan shirin Birtaniya na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai kuma muna nan a rana don gaya muku cewa 'ba za mu taɓa jure muku ba.'
A cikin sakon da ya aika wa taron da suka yi farin ciki, ya ce: 'Ina son a kafa tsarin siyasarmu, wanda zai yi wa Birtaniya ta shirin ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai, a kan gungumen azaba.
"Muna kira ga al'umma su kare wannan kasa da ta ba mu nasara wajen cire Birtaniya daga Tarayyar Turai kuma ba za mu huta ba har sai mun mallaki, jagorancin, da girman kai na Birtaniya".
A halin yanzu, waɗanda suke son zama a cikin iyali na Ingila sun yi tafiya zuwa Birmingham kafin su tsaya awa biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Masu zanga-zangar canji sun yi ta tayar da tutarsu a cikin Jam'iyyar Tory suna neman Birtaniya ta bar EU bayan da suka kaddamar da wata kungiya a karshen mako.
'Yan jam'iyyar Labour da suka hada da Lord Adonis sun soki yadda suka bi ka'idojin da suka gabata kan batutuwan tsaro da suka fuskanta a taron jam'iyyar a lokacin da taron ya fara.
Ya kara da cewa, "Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa muna da fasaha da kuma cewa dukkan fasahar Kanada ta ci gaba, iyakoki ba su da haraji, harkokin kasuwanci a kan iyakar Ireland".
'Ba gaskiya ba ne.
Babu abin da ya fi kyau kamar kawar da Ingila,' in ji shi.
Warren ya yi shirin "tunanin" takararsa
A cewar Sanata Elizabeth Warren, "za ta yi tunani sosai game da takarar shugaban kasa" bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar The Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa dan majalisa dan Democrat na Massachusetts ya yi jawabi a gidan wasan kwaikwayo na West Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman takara ta biyu a watan Nuwamba inda ya yi gwagwarmaya da Geoff Diehl, wanda ya kasance mataimakin shugaban aikin Trump a Massachusetts a shekarar 2016.
An yi ta magana a cikin jita-jita daban-daban cewa zai iya yin gwagwarmaya da Trump a cikin 2020.
A taron da ya gudana a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne taro na 36 da ya yi da masu jefa kuri'a a yankin da ya yi amfani da tsarin majalisar dokoki tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani mai halartar taron ya tambaye shi ko yana shirin yin takara a matsayin shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa: "Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su yi sarauta a kan gwamnatinmu da ta rabu inda za a yi sarauta ta mata".
An kama wani a cikin wani rikici da ya haifar da mutuwar Sims a LSU.
A ranar Asabar, 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge, La., sun sanar da cewa an kama wani mai zargin da ake zargi da aikata laifi a cikin wani tashin hankali da ya haifar da mutuwar dan wasan kwallon kwando na jami'ar LSU, Wayde Sims.
'Yan sanda na Baton Rouge sun sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, da karfe 11 na safe.
Sun wallafa bidiyo game da tashin hankali da ya faru a ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako don su san mutumin da ke cikin hotunan.
An harbe Sims, mai shekaru 20, a kusa da Jami'ar Kudancin Amurka a cikin sa'o'i na farko na Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya mutu ne daga wata harbe-harbe a kai kuma ya mutu a wurin da aka harbe shi", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda, Murphy J. Paul, a cewar 247sports a ranar Asabar.
Wayde ya zo ne don ya ceci abokinsa kuma Simpson ya yi masa baƙar magana.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya yarda cewa ya kasance a wurin da aka yi harbi da bindiga kuma ya yarda ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da yin laifi ba kuma an tura shi zuwa Sashen 'Yan Sanda na East Baton Rouge Parish.
Matashi mai tsayi na mita 2 ya biyo baya a Baton Rouge, Sims ya buga wasanni 32 inda ya fara 10 a bara kuma yana da matsakaicin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da sakewa 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Gasar Grand Prix ta Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusan lashe kofin duniya bayan da kungiyar ta amince da shi a matsayin wanda ya lashe gasar ta lashe Sebastian Vettel
Ya bayyana sarai tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya ci gaba da yin tseren a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar har Mercedes ta tabbatar da cewa tana da babban tasiri a gasar.
Tun daga farkon tseren, Bottas ya fara da kyau kuma ya kusan doke Hamilton yayin da ya yi gwagwarmaya don matsayi a cikin wasanni biyu na farko kuma ya sa Vettel ya kai hari ga abokin aikinsa.
Vettel ya tafi wurin juyawa na farko kuma ya bar Hamilton a baya - wani babban abin da aka yanke shawara.
Mercedes sun yi kyau kuma sun bi Vettel, amma Hamilton ya ci gaba bayan ya yi karo da Ferrari kuma ya yi kuskure a cikin direba, wanda ya bar wata rata kuma ya bar shi a matsayin mai gwagwarmaya a kusurwar ta uku.
Max Verstappen ya fara daga baya kuma ya zo na bakwai bayan ya fara motsawa a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Domin ya jagoranci mafi yawan tseren yayin da yake tafiya a kan ƙafafunsa don ya yi niyyar kammala ta hanyar Kimi Raikkonen a matsayin na huɗu.
Ta kai ga filin motsa jiki a raga na 44 amma ba ta iya ƙara saurin ta a raga takwas na ƙarshe inda Raikkonen ya zama na huɗu.
Rana ce mai wuya domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai kyau a ƙarshen mako kuma ya zama mutumin kirki.
Hamilton ya ce: "Ƙungiyar ta yi aiki mai ban mamaki don samun na farko da na biyu".
Wannan magana ce ta jiki da ba ta dace ba.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya soki Sanata Dianne Feinstein a lokacin da ta ke neman takara a ranar Asabar saboda ta nace cewa ba ita ce ta bayyana wasikar da Christine Blasey Ford ta rubuta game da zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, na lalata da ita ba.
A lokacin da yake jawabi a zabensa a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Baƙi ba, amma ya ba da shawarar cewa abin da ya faru a Majalisar ya nuna cewa mutane "marasa kyau ne, marasa adalci, kuma marasa aminci".
"Abin da zai iya faruwa kuma mai kyau shi ne a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan a majalisar, inda kake ganin fushi, ganin mutane masu fushi, da mugunta, da zalunci, da rashin aminci".
"Idan ka ga abin da aka yi da kuma abin da aka yi da ba a ba da izini ba, za ka ce, 'Oh, ban taɓa yin hakan ba.
Ban yi hakan ba".
Ka tuna?
Dianne Feinstein, ka taba buga wannan ba tare da izini ba?
Ka tuna da amsarsa... wanda ya wallafa wannan rubutun ba tare da izini ba; "eh, eh, me?
Ba haka ba.
Ban taɓa yin hakan ba".
Yana da kyau, amma ba kaɗan ba.
Mun bayyana ba tare da izini ba...A'a, ba mu fitar da izini ba", in ji shi, don faranta wa mai zane rai.
An aika wa Feinstein da wasika game da zargin da Ford ya yi game da Kavanaugh a watan Yuli, kuma an bayyana shi ba tare da izini ba a farkon watan Satumba, amma Feinstein ya yi watsi da sanarwar ba tare da izini ba daga ofishinsa.
"Ban taba ɓoye zargin Dr. Ford ba, ban bayyana labarinsa ba", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin, kamar yadda jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Ya ce in yi hakan a ɓoye, kuma na yi abin da ya ce".
Amma shugaban ya yi rashin amincewa da ƙin yarda da shi, wanda ya ce a lokacin da ake zanga-zangar Asabar da dare: "Ina gaya maka, wannan mummunan magana ce ta jiki.
Wataƙila bai yi hakan ba, amma na ga munanan maganganun da ake yi".
Da yake ci gaba da kare da'awar da ake yi wa mai jiran shugaban Kotun Koli, wanda aka zargi da lalata da mata uku, shugaban ya ce 'yan Democrat za su yi amfani da zargin don amfanin kansu.
"Sun ƙuduri aniya su dawo da kansu da dukan ƙarfin da za su iya.
Yana ganin mugunta, mugunta, rashin kula da waɗanda za su cutar da su, wanda za su iya rinjayar su su sami iko da kuma iko".
Gasar Elite League: Dundee Stars ta ci Belfast Giants 5-3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci raga biyu da kungiyar Giants ta buga a Dundee
Dundee Stars ta sake yin wani sabon abu a gasar Elite League a ranar Juma'a lokacin da ta buga da Belfast Giants a wasan da suka yi a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da cin nasara a raga biyu a kan kwallon da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier suka yi.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun sa ƙungiyar ta samu nasara kafin Dwyer ya sake sa Giants su jagoranci.
Francois Bouchard ya ci kwallaye a raga tare da Dundee kafin Luka Lundvald Nielsen ya ci nasara.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da ya lashe gasar Elite League a kakar wasa ta Adam Keefe, wanda ya ci nasara a kan Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka hadu a kakar wasa ta farko, inda Giants suka ci nasara a wasanni uku na farko.
Dwyer ya ci kwallo a wasan farko a minti 3:35 da Kendall McFaull ya buga, inda David Rutherford ya ba Beauvillier kwallo kuma ya ci kwallo ta biyu bayan minti kadan.
A farkon wasan da ya fi dacewa, Sullivan ya sake dawo da tawagar a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba da kwallon ga Cownie kuma ya ci nasara a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da ci gaba da jagorancin Giants a farkon wasan da ya ci kwallaye na biyu na wasan a daren da ya gabata a ƙarshen wasan.
A lokacin da aka sake buga wasan, Bouchard ya sake samun nasara a wasan da aka yi a minti 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi aiki tare don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee damar yin wasan farko na wasan kafin ƙarshen wasan kuma ya sa ƙungiyar ta ci wasan a minti na ƙarshe.
Giants, da suka ci nasara a wasanni hudu a cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su ziyarci Milton Keynes a wasan da zai gudana a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa daruruwan mutane a cikin jirgin zasu iya tsira daga girgizar ƙasa
Mai kula da jirgin sama na Indonesia zai zama jarumi bayan ya mutu don tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama mai dauke da ɗaruruwan mutane ya sauka a ƙasa.
Fiye da mutane 800 sun mutu kuma an yi gargadin cewa sun bace bayan wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta afku a tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta ƙarshe ta ci gaba da addabar yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun bar ragowar gine-gine a Palu.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun yi kokarin ceton rayukansu, wani saurayi mai shekaru 21 mai suna Anthonius Gunawan Agung ya ƙi barin aikinsa a cikin hasumiyar da ke girgiza sosai saboda iska mai iska da iska ta yi a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri Palu.
Ya ci gaba da aikinsa don tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama na Batik Air Flight 6321, wanda ya kai ga samun wuta, zai iya tashi lafiya.
A ƙarshe, ya yi tsalle daga cikin hasumiyar jirgin sama, yana tsammanin zai faɗi.
Ta mutu a asibiti.
Kakakin hukumar kula da jiragen sama ta Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin na iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, kamar yadda ABC News ta Australia ta ruwaito.
Mun shirya jirgin ruwa daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan don a kai shi babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin baƙin ciki, ya mutu a wannan lokacin kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
Ya ƙara da cewa: "Mun yi baƙin ciki ƙwarai".
A halin yanzu, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin mutuwar zai iya ƙaru zuwa dubbai saboda Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ce ba a kammala isa ga biranen Donggala, Sigi da Boutong ba.
Kakakin hukumar, Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, ya ce: "Lambar ta ci gaba da ƙaruwa daga jikin mutane da yawa da ke rufewa a lokacin da sauran mutane ba su da damar yin hakan".
Tashin da ya kai mita shida ya lalata Palu inda ake sa ran binne wasu a kabarin jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jirgin saman soja da na sufuri suna kawo kayan aiki da kayan aiki.
Risa Kusuma, wata mace mai shekaru 35, ta shaida wa Sky News: "Kowace mintiyar da ta wuce akwai masu zuwa don su kawo maka taimako.
Rashin ruwa mai kyau ba shi da yawa.
An yi fashi a dukan shaguna".
Jan Gelfand, shugaban kungiyar agaji ta Red Cross ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN: "Kungiyar agaji ta Indonesiya Red Cross tana neman hanyoyin da za ta taimaka wa wadanda suka tsira amma ba mu san abin da za su samu ba.
"Ya riga ya zama haɗari, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban Indonesia, Joko Widodo, ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi kuma ya gaya wa sojojin kasar: "Ina rokon ku duka ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala duk wani aikin ceto.
Shin kun shirya?" CNN ta ruwaito.
Tun da farko a wannan shekara, Indonesia ta sha wahala daga girgizar ƙasa a Lombok inda ya kashe mutane sama da 550.
Hadarin jirgin sama a Micronesia: Kamfanin Air Niugini ya bayyana cewa mutum daya ya bace bayan ya fada cikin hatsari
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ya yi hatsarin jirgin sama a yankin Pacific a Micronesia yanzu yana bayyana cewa an rasa wani mutum, bayan an riga an ce an cire dukkan fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin sama 47 daga wurin jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Kamfanin Air Niugini ya bayyana a cikin wata sanarwa da ya fitar cewa a ranar Asabar da yamma, ba ta iya gano abokin aikin ba.
Kamfanin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin gwamnati, asibitoci da kuma bincike don gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin sama bai amsa ba da sauri ga buƙatar samar da ƙarin bayani game da abokin aikin kamar shekarun sa ko asalinsa.
Jirgin ruwa na yankin ya taimaka wajen kama wasu fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin sama bayan jirgin ya fadi a ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a tashar jirgin saman Chuuk.
Jami'ai sun ce an kai mutane bakwai asibiti a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, kuma duk suna lafiya.
Dalilin wannan hatsarin shi ne cewa ba a san ainihin abin da ya faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da rundunar sojin ruwa na Amurka sun yi amannar cewa jirgin ya fadi a kwarin jim kadan bayan ya tashi.
Wasu shaidu sun yi zaton jirgin ya yi kuskure.
Wani abokinsa na Amurka, Bill Jaynes, ya ce jirgin ya sauka a ƙasa mai zurfi.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Jayness.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu da suka yi nasarar shiga cikin ruwa sun yi nasara sosai har zuwa lokacin da suka fito cikin gaggawa daga jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Ta ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma sun yi ihu kuma ta ji rauni a kai.
