Shugaban majalisar dokokin kasar Nancy Pelosi ta kira wanda aka nada a matsayin shugaban kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, "bawan zuciya" kuma ta ce bai dace da shi ba ta hanyar ɗabi'a don yin aiki a kotun koli.
Pelosi ta yi wannan furucin ne a wata hira da ta yi a ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune Festival da ke Austin, Texas.
"Ba zan iya yin komai ba sai na yi mamakin ko wata mace ta taɓa yin wannan, ta ce 'ta yi baƙin ciki,'" in ji Pelosi game da yadda ta amsa shaidar Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ta musanta zargin da ake yi mata na lalata da Dr. Christine Blasey Ford lokacin da su biyun matasa ne.
A farkon shaidarsa, Kavanaugh ya yi fushi sosai, har ya yi ihu da fushi lokacin da yake magana game da iyalinsa da shekarun makarantar sakandare.
Ya yi watsi da 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat a kwamitin, yana mai cewa zargin da ake masa "mai ban mamaki da kuma neman kashe shi" ya fito ne daga masu zanga-zangar da suka yi fushi da Hillary Clinton ta lashe zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
Pelosi ta ce ta yi imanin cewa shaidar Kavanaugh ta tabbatar da cewa ba ta aiki a matsayin babban alƙali na Kotun Koli ba, saboda ta nuna cewa tana da tsayayya da dimokiradiyya.
"Ina ganin ya yi murabus da kansa saboda maganganunsa da kuma yadda ya yi wa dangin Clinton da 'yan Democrat laifi", in ji shi.
Pelosi ta yi tambaya a kan ko za ta iya ƙoƙarin rinjayar Kavanaugh lokacin da aka amince da ita kuma ko 'yan Democrat za su sami rinjaye a majalisa.
Pelosi ta ce: "Ina so in gaya muku cewa idan ba ta gaya wa majalisar ko FBI gaskiya ba, to, ba ta kamata ta yi aiki a Kotun Koli ba, amma ta kamata ta yi aiki a kotun da take yanzu".
Kavanaugh a halin yanzu alkali ne a kotun daukaka kara ta D.C.
Pelosi ta kara da cewa a matsayinta na dimokiradiyya, tana da damuwa cewa Kavanaugh zai iya yin hukunci a kan Dokar Adalci ta Kiwon Lafiya a kan Roe v. Wade, wanda aka ɗauka a matsayin adalci mai bin ƙa'idodin gargajiya.
A shari'ar tabbatar da shi, Kavanaugh ya yi watsi da tambayar ko zai iya yin watsi da wasu hukuncin Kotun Koli.
Pelosi ta ce: "Wannan ba lokaci ba ne na zama bawan zuciya, wanda ke da 'yancin kai a kotu kuma yana tsammanin za mu ce, 'Wannan ba daidai ba ne.'"
