Ta yaya cinikayya ta Amurka da China za ta iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
Yaƙin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China ya rufe baki kuma idan yaƙin ya zo ba tare da an gama shi ba, rashin fahimtar juna tsakanin kasashen biyu na iya zama fa'ida ga Beijing na dogon lokaci, a cewar masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ne ya fara gabatar da haraji a farkon wannan shekarar kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa daga kasar Sin, ciki har da kayan ado, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi mahimmancin yarjejeniyar ita ce a wannan makon da aka gabatar da sabon tsarin haraji wanda ya shafi darajar dala biliyan 200 (£ 150 biliyan) na kayayyaki, wanda ya haifar da haraji kusan rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta amsa daidai, inda ta kwanan nan ta sanya haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari akan kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
Kasar Sin ta yi niyyar daidaita matakan da Amurka ta dauka, kuma tana da tattalin arziki na biyu a duniya kuma ba za ta iya kasawa ba.
Don sake dawo da gwamnatin Washington yana nufin cewa akwai buƙatu, amma a fili yin sujada ga Amurka na iya zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, Shugaban China.
Kuma masana har yanzu suna cewa idan Beijing ta yi aiki da kyau, matsin lamba na yakin kasuwanci da Amurka zai iya taimakawa China a cikin dogon lokaci kuma ya rage cinikayyar da ke tsakanin manyan tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Idan Washington ko Beijing suka yanke shawara ta siyasa da sauri, za su iya kafa wata manufa ta sauya manufa ga kasashen biyu kuma hakan zai zama mummunan ga masu kallon yakin kamar yadda suka amince da shi a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, mataimakin mai bincike na Asiya na Cibiyar New American Security, wadda ta kafa wani rukuni na masana.
Syria ta "shirya" don karbar 'yan gudun hijira da ba su dawo ba, a cewar Ministan Harkokin Wajen
Syria ta ce tana shirye don samun 'yan gudun hijira da suka so su dawo kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta shafe fiye da shekaru bakwai tana fama da yaƙi.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta Tarayyar Turai, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Turai, Walid al-Moualem, ya ce yanayin rayuwa a kasar yana inganta.
"A yau, a ƙasar akwai zaman lafiya da tsaro saboda an ɗauki mataki na yaki da ta'addanci".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da sake gina wasu yankunan da masu fashewa suka lalata domin dawo da rayuwa ta yau da kullum.
Ana samun cikakkun umarni ga 'yan gudun hijira da ke son komawa ƙasarsu da yardar rai saboda barazanar ta'addanci da kuma dabarun tattalin arziki marasa kyau da ke shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria ta yi wa kowa laifi na sake gina kasar da yaki ya yi.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai iya karɓar taimakon da aka ba da ta hanyar dokokin ƙasashe da suka karfafa 'yan tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup da aka gudanar a birnin Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 inda ta lashe gasar cin kofin Amurka ta karshe ta hanyar maki 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a gasar Le Golf National da aka gudanar a waje da Paris, Faransa.
A halin yanzu, Amurka ta sha kashi shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder Cup a Turai tun 1993.
Turai ta sake karbar lambar yabo lokacin da kyaftin din tawagar Denmark karkashin jagorancin Thomas Bjorn ya kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don cin nasara a Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala sosai daga gasar, ya jefa kwallonsa cikin ruwa a karo na 3 daga cikin 16, kuma ya yi rashin nasara a wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Mai wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya ci nasara a duk fafatawa, ya zama mai wasan 1 daga cikin 4 da ya ci nasara fiye da 5-0-0 tun lokacin da gasar ta yanzu ta fara a 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya ci 5&4 inda ya ci gaba da samun mafi ƙarancin maki a tawagar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan duniya mai cin nasara, ya ci nasara 2-1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda zai iya zama wasan Ryder Cup na ƙarshe.
Tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cups, Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasan Turai mafi girma a gasar cin kofin Turai tare da maki 25.5 a cikin aikinsa.
"A yawancin lokaci ba na son yin kuka amma yau ba na son yin hakan.
Shekara ce mai muhimmanci.
Ina godiya sosai ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya amince da ni.
Ina farin ciki sosai, ina farin cikin dawo da kofin.
Game da tawagar kuma ina farin cikin taimaka", in ji Garcia cikin farin ciki bayan nasarar gasar Turai.
Ya ba da aikin ga wani dan wasansa na ƙasar ɗaya mai suna John Ram wanda ya lashe gasar golf ta Amurka, Tiger Woods, 2 zuwa 1 a wasan da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Na girma ina ganin cewa ina da alfahari sosai da na ci Tiger Woods.
Woods ya sha kaye a wasanni hudu da ya gabata a Faransa kuma yanzu ya sha kaye 13-21-3 a gasar cin kofin Ryder.
Wani abu mai ban mamaki shi ne cewa daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na kowane lokaci, wanda ya lashe manyan kofuna 14 ya kasance na biyu bayan Jack Nicklaus.
An yi wa tawagar Amurka ta yi wa'azi a duk karshen mako don samun damar daidaitawa da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf a kowane wasa.
Kyaftin na tawagar Amurka, Jim Furyk, ya ce bayan wasan da bai yi wa tawagarsa kyau ba, "Ba na alfahari da kasancewa 'yan wasan, sun yi gwagwarmaya da kyau.
A wannan safiya, muna matsa lamba a kan tawagar Turai.
Mun rabu.
Muna godiya sosai ga Thomas.
Shi kyawawan kyaftin ne.
Dukkan 'yan wasan 12 sun yi kyau.
Za mu sake haduwa a matsayin ƙungiya, zan yi iyakacin ƙoƙarin da zan iya don samun damar zuwa gasar PGA ta Amurka da kuma Kwamitin Gasar Ryder Cup kuma za mu yi nisa.
Ina son waɗannan 'yan wasan 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftin nasu.
